snippet.title: Best VGM 2095 - Bravely Default - Land of Radiant Flowers
snippet.description:
See also;

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo 3DS
Bravely Default : Flying Fairy (2012)
Land of Radiant Flowers
